<h1>Welcome to Steve's Sock Shack!</h1>

<h2>In 2015, Steve G. fullfilled his dream by creating a store where people can express thier feelings and creativity...through socks!</h2>
<h2>The more stylish and sillier the sock, the better!</h2>
<hr>
<p><%= link_to "Add a New Sock", new_product_path %></p>
<hr>

<% if @products != nil %>
  <h3>Here's a list of our available socks!</h3>
    <% @products.each do |product| %>
      <h4><%= link_to product.name, product_path(product) %>: $ <%= product.cost %></h4>
    <% end %>
<% else %>
  <h2>No socks...yet</h2>
<% end %>
<hr>

<h3>Shop local! Here's a list of socks made in the USA</h3>
<% @usaproducts.each do |product| %>
  <h4><%= link_to product.name, product_path(product) %>: $ <%= product.cost %></h4>
<% end %>
<hr>



<p>If your sock game is wack, then go to Steve's Sock Shack!</p>
